column5: Does anyone know where I can get a map of Restoule Lake (Provincial Park)? I checked (and emailed) Jack at Adventure Fishing Maps, but I'm not sure if they have it or not as its not listed on their website.  Any help is much appreciated!
http://www.anglersatlas.com/lakes/25323/  Jamie.. if you don't have an account or can't open it to print it out.. PM me an email address..  You can also buy it laminated for $7.99
